  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A famous recipe from @UUID[Compendium.folken-games-fantasy-chef.folken-games-fantasy-cooking-journal-entries.JournalEntry.sqEE4iaGlPaZwFLC]{Savage Sustenance}</p><p>Provides @UUID[Compendium.pf1.spells.jnlr9cuepka1l26e]{Enlarge Person} for 30 minutes.</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">The recipe for this hearty creation was gifted to me by Zokar Elkarid, the owner of Ravengo’s own Laughing Demon! While it isn’t his signature horror-themed fare, Zokar told me this is what he enjoys on his day off. Tater tot hotdish combines golden tater tots, succulent ground meat, and a symphony of vegetables, bound together by a velvety sauce. It is a feast fit for champions, promising satisfaction and nourishment after a hard-fought battle or a day of epic adventures.</span></p><img src=\"modules/folken-games-fantasy-chef/images/tater_tot_hot_dish_arcanograph_dd_magic_item.jpg\" />",
